quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  56,1,"When the Event will come to pass"
  56,2,"– and then there will be no one to deny its occurrence –"{1},footnotes:1:1
  56,3,"(a calamitous Event) that shall turn things upside down:"{1},footnotes:1:1
  56,4,"when the earth will suddenly shake with a terrible shaking,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  56,5,"and the mountains will crumble"
  56,6,"and will scatter abroad into fine dust."
  56,7,"You shall then become three groups."{1},footnotes:1:1
  56,8,"The People on the Right: and how fortunate will be the People on the Right!"{1},footnotes:1:1
  56,9,"And the People on the Left: and how miserable will be the People on the Left!"{1},footnotes:1:1
  56,10,"As for the Foremost, they will be the foremost!"{1},footnotes:1:1